(FizzBuzz! do
  i = 1
  while i < 16 do
    found = 0
    if mod(i, 15) = 0 do
      put("FizzBuzz")
      found = 1
    end
    if found = 0 do
      if mod(i, 3) = 0 do
        put("Fizz")
        found = 1
      end
    end
    if found = 0 do
      if mod(i, 5) = 0 do
        put("Buzz")
        found = 1
      end
    end
    if found = 0 do
      put(i)
    end
    i = i + 1
  end
end)
